<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lath" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lath,</orth> a slip of wood: <cit><quote>dagger of l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 4.2.136" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. IV, 2, 136</bibl></cit> and <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.151" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 151</bibl>. <cit><quote>a sword, though made of a l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.2.2" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 2, 2</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>have your l. glued within your sheath,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.1.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 1, 41</bibl></cit> (== sword, in contempt). <cit><quote>bow of l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 1.4.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 4, 5</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>